text: This obsoletes IRM 25.23.7, Identity Protection and Victim Assistance, AUR Identity Theft Processing

The material relating to the policy and guidance previously contained in IRM 25.23.7, Identity Protection and Victim Assistance, AUR Identity Theft Processing is being incorporated into IRM 25.23.10, Compliance Identity Theft Case Processing.
Applies to all employees working in Identity Theft Victim Assistance (ITVA)-Compliance
